parameters: The statue depicts a tall, broad shouldered knight.
He wears a flat mask, devoid of features.
The text on this statue is worn and faded. You are only
able to read fragments of the text:
\c[5]Our Pale Father. . . Faceless watcher of the night. . .
Guardian of dreamers. . . Lover of the Sun. . .
There is a plaque holding the text that is raised,
as if it can be pushed. Do you push the plaque?
The monstrous, demonic statue menacingly looms over you.
It feels as if you are being watched.
